ates are modified by uniform rotation through the Coriolis acceleration. Study\nof the effect of differential rotation is dedicated to a forthcoming paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2009 13:22:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2009 11:32:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
